high_descs: Move to the right to face the microwave next to the refrigerator.
Pick the spoon up from off of the counter.
Move to the left to face the stovetop.
Place the spoon in the pot on the stovetop.
Pick up the pot from off of the stovetop.
Move to the left to face the empty counter next to the toaster.
Place the pot on the counter top.
anns.task_desc: Place the pot with the spoon on top of the counter.

high_descs: Go forward toward the dishwasher, then turn right to face the microwave.
Pick up the spoon on the counter, to the left of the microwave.
Turn around, go forward, then turn right to face the stove.
Put the spoon in the pot on the left corner of the stove.
Pick up the pot with the spoon in it.
Turn around, and go to the counter with the toaster on it.
Put the pot on the counter, to the right of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with a spoon in it on the counter.

high_descs: Move to the counter to the right of the sink to the left of the fridge
Pick up a spoon from the counter
Move to the stove to the left of the sink
Place the spoon in a pot on the stove
Pick up the pot with the spoon from the stove
Move to the counter to the right of the toaster
Place the pot on the counter
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with a spoon next to the toaster.
